---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import { buttonVariants } from "@/components/ui/button";
import { MoveLeft } from "lucide-react";

---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - PenguFit AI">
  <main class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl py-20 px-4">
    <div class="mx-auto">
      <a   
        href="/"
        class:list={[
          buttonVariants({ variant: "secondary" })
        ]}
      >
        <MoveLeft size={16} />
        Back to Home
        </a>
      <header class="my-8">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold">Privacy Policy</h1>
      </header>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
          <strong>Last updated: August 1, 2025</strong>
        </p>
        <p>
          This Privacy Policy explains how PenguFit ("we", "our", or "us")
          collects, uses, and protects your personal information when you use
          our calorie tracking application ("App").
        </p>
        <p>
          By using PenguFit, you agree to the collection and use of information
          in accordance with this policy.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>
          We collect the following types of information when you use our App:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
          <li>
            <strong>Email address</strong> – used for authentication and
            communication.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Current weight, height, target weight, and fitness goals</strong
            > – used to provide personalized recommendations and tracking features.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Usage data</strong> – including your activity and progress
            within the app.
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          We do <strong>not</strong> collect sensitive health data or identifiers
          beyond the information listed above.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use your information to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
          <li>
            Provide core app functionalities, such as tracking weight and goals.
          </li>
          <li>Personalize your experience based on your goals and data.</li>
          <li>Offer access to AI-powered food and receipt scanning.</li>
          <li>
            Manage subscriptions and payments via third-party providers.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-4">3. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>We use the following third-party services:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
          <li>
            <strong>Supabase</strong> – for user authentication and database
            management.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Lemon Squeezy</strong> – for processing premium subscription
            payments.
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          These providers have their own privacy policies and may collect
          information necessary to perform their services.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-4">4. Data Storage and Security</h2>
        <p>
          Your information is securely stored in Supabase databases. We
          implement reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect
          your personal data from unauthorized access or disclosure.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-4">5. International Use</h2>
        <p>
          PenguFit is available worldwide. Regardless of where you use our App,
          your information may be processed in countries outside your own,
          including in the United States and Europe, where our third-party
          services are based.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-4">6. Age Restrictions</h2>
        <p>
          The App is intended for users aged <strong>18 and older</strong>. We
          do not knowingly collect information from individuals under 18. If we
          learn that we have collected personal data from a minor, we will take
          steps to remove it promptly.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-4">7. Account Access and Deletion</h2>
        <p>
          Currently, users may log out of the App at any time. At this time, we
          do not offer automatic account deletion. To request deletion of your
          account and data, please contact us directly.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-4">8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Any significant
          changes will be communicated within the App or via email. Continued
          use of the App after such updates constitutes your acceptance of the
          new terms.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-4">9. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please
          contact us at:<br />
          <strong>contact@pengufit.com</strong>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
